---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About the Institute"
  description="Idara Ulum-Al-Qur'an was established in 1984 at Aligarh Muslim University, following the scholarly tradition of Imam Hamid al-Din Farahi."
  canonicalUrl="/en/about/"
>
  <main class="container page-content">

    <nav class="breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
      <a href="/en/">Home</a>
      <span>›</span>
      <span>About</span>
    </nav>

    <h1>About the Institute</h1>

    <div class="page-grid">
      <article class="page-body">

        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>Idara Ulum-Al-Qur'an is an independent academic institute established in 1984 at Aligarh Muslim University, Aligarh. The institute is dedicated to the research, teaching, and publication of works in the field of Qur'anic sciences.</p>

        <h2>Intellectual Tradition</h2>
        <p>The institute follows the scholarly methodology of Imam Hamid al-Din Farahi (1863–1930), one of the most original Qur'anic scholars of the modern era. Farahi's approach emphasised the internal coherence and thematic unity (<em>nazm</em>) of the Qur'an. His student, Maulana Amin Ahsan Islahi, carried this tradition forward through his monumental tafsir <em>Tadabbur-i-Qur'an</em>.</p>

        <h2>Activities</h2>
        <p>The institute carries out the following activities:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Publishing the biannual peer-reviewed journal <em>Ulum al-Qur'an</em> since 1985</li>
          <li>Organising annual Qur'anic seminars and monthly scholars' seminars</li>
          <li>Conducting national competitions in Qur'anic studies</li>
          <li>Publishing books and research papers on Qur'anic themes</li>
          <li>Running a special lecture series on Qur'anic sciences</li>
          <li>Maintaining a specialised library of Qur'anic literature</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Location</h2>
        <p>The institute is located within the campus of Aligarh Muslim University, one of India's premier central universities, in Aligarh, Uttar Pradesh.</p>

      </article>

      <aside class="page-sidebar">
        <div class="sidebar-card">
          <h3>Quick Facts</h3>
          <ul class="fact-list">
            <li><span class="fact-label">Founded</span><span class="fact-value">1984</span></li>
            <li><span class="fact-label">Location</span><span class="fact-value">AMU, Aligarh</span></li>
            <li><span class="fact-label">Journal</span><span class="fact-value">Since 1985</span></li>
            <li><span class="fact-label">Volumes</span><span class="fact-value">39</span></li>
            <li><span class="fact-label">Languages</span><span class="fact-value">Urdu, English, Hindi</span></li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="sidebar-card">
          <h3>Related Links</h3>
          <ul class="link-list">
            <li><a href="/en/journal/">Biannual Journal</a></li>
            <li><a href="/en/publications/">Publications</a></li>
            <li><a href="/en/seminars/">Seminars</a></li>
            <li><a href="/en/contact/">Contact Us</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>

  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
.page-content {
  padding-top: 2.5rem;
  padding-bottom: 4rem;
}

.breadcrumb {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.5rem;
  font-size: 0.85rem;
  color: var(--color-muted);
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}

.breadcrumb a {
  color: var(--color-link);
}

.breadcrumb a:hover {
  text-decoration: underline;
}

h1 {
  font-size: 2.25rem;
  color: var(--color-primary);
  margin-bottom: 2rem;
  padding-bottom: 1rem;
  border-bottom: 2px solid var(--color-border);
}

.page-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 280px;
  gap: 3rem;
  align-items: start;
}

.page-body h2 {
  font-size: 1.3rem;
  color: var(--color-primary);
  margin-top: 2rem;
  margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
}

.page-body p {
  font-size: 1rem;
  line-height: 1.85;
  color: var(--color-text);
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.page-body ul {
  padding-left: 1.5rem;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.page-body ul li {
  font-size: 1rem;
  line-height: 1.85;
  color: var(--color-text);
  margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
}

.page-body em {
  color: var(--color-primary);
  font-style: italic;
}

.sidebar-card {
  background: var(--color-white);
  border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  border-radius: 8px;
  padding: 1.25rem;
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}

.sidebar-card h3 {
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  color: var(--color-muted);
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
  padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
}

.fact-list {
  list-style: none;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 0.6rem;
}

.fact-list li {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  font-size: 0.9rem;
}

.fact-label {
  color: var(--color-muted);
}

.fact-value {
  color: var(--color-text);
  font-weight: 600;
  text-align: right;
}

.link-list {
  list-style: none;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 0.5rem;
}

.link-list a {
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  color: var(--color-link);
}

.link-list a:hover {
  text-decoration: underline;
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  h1 {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
  }

  .page-grid {
    display: block;
  }

  .page-sidebar {
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
  }
}
</style>